<Base
  title="Takes: Priority Filters &amp; Belief Change Log | Jevan Goldsmith"
  description="Where Jevan Goldsmith files his takes: priority filters and a public log of beliefs he has changed."
  canonical="https://jevangoldsmith.com/takes.html"
  pageType="CollectionPage"
>
<main class="takes-main">
    <section class="takes-hero">
        <p class="takes-eyebrow">Takes</p>
        <h1>Where my takes live.</h1>
        <p>Two running logs of how I decide and how I update. One sorts what matters from what only feels urgent. The other tracks beliefs I have changed and why.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="takes-grid" aria-label="Takes collections">
        <a href="/important-or-not.html" class="takes-card">
            <p class="takes-card-eyebrow">Decision Filter</p>
            <h2>Important or Not</h2>
            <p>Sorting signal from noise: what actually matters versus what only feels urgent or attractive.</p>
            <span class="takes-card-cta">Open the filter &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/changed-my-mind.html" class="takes-card">
            <p class="takes-card-eyebrow">Belief Change Log</p>
            <h2>Changed My Mind</h2>
            <p>A public record of ideas I have updated, softened, reversed, or stopped believing.</p>
            <span class="takes-card-cta">See the reversals &rarr;</span>
        </a>
